@@ -1,16 +1,31 @@
 Changelog
 =========
 
 master
 ------
 
+* Fix TypedDict stub generation for TypedDicts nested inside generic containers
+  like ``List[TypedDict]`` or ``Dict[str, TypedDict]``. Previously these would
+  produce stubs with ``DUMMY_NAME`` references instead of properly generated
+  TypedDict class stubs.
+
+* Fix ``max_typed_dict_size`` not being propagated through nested containers
+  (list, set, tuple, defaultdict). Dicts nested inside these containers now
+  properly respect the ``max_typed_dict_size`` setting.
+
+* Empty dicts now generate ``Dict[Any, Any]`` instead of an empty TypedDict,
+  which is more intuitive.
+
+* Add ``rewrite_TypedDict`` method to the base ``TypeRewriter`` class, allowing
+  any TypeRewriter subclass to handle TypedDicts.
+
 
 19.11.2
 -------
 
 * Disable TypedDict generation by default for now, since it breaks `--apply`.
 
 
 19.11.1
 -------
 
